    <comment>New package: kimi-code 0.27.0

Kimi Code, Moonshot AI's command-line coding agent (MIT). Packaged from the
self-contained npm bundle; the interactive shell backend (node-pty 1.1.0) is
compiled from source offline with node-addon-api 7.1.1 as a vendored native
addon. Runtime code search uses the system ripgrep and fd.

Built for Leap 16.0/aarch64 with 0 rpmlint badness, source_validator clean,
%check (kimi --version) passes. ExclusiveArch x86_64 aarch64 (native addon).</comment>
